  [ Run times consist of 0.060 seconds GC time, and 0.618 seconds non-GC time. ]
  100.44% CPU
  7 forms interpreted
  391,349,920 bytes consed")
 (p "Now for the optimized version:")
 (pre :class "code-block-source-pre"
